%N A180309 Decimal expansion of the torsional rigidity constant for a square shaft.
%C A180309 No closed form is known.
%F A180309 Equals (1 - (192*Sum_{n>=1} (tanh(((-1 + 2*n)*Pi)/2)/(-1 + 2*n)^5))/Pi^5)/3.
%F A180309 Equals 1/3 - 62*zeta(5)/Pi^5 + (128/Pi^5)*Sum_{n>=1} 1/((2*n-1)^5*(exp((2*n-1)*Pi)+1)). - _Hideaki Nagamine_, May 05 2026
